  <title>Gio.PasswordSave</title>
  <p><link xref="Gio.PasswordSave"/> is used to indicate the lifespan of a saved password.</p>  <p>#Gvfs stores passwords in the Gnome keyring when this flag allows it
to, and later retrieves it again from there.</p>

<terms>
<item>
<title><code>PasswordSave.NEVER</code></title>
  <p>never save a password.</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>PasswordSave.FOR_SESSION</code></title>
  <p>save a password for the session.</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>PasswordSave.PERMANENTLY</code></title>
  <p>save a password permanently.</p>
</item>
